## Exports

### Component Exports

Components are exported individually:

```typescript
// packages/ui/src/components/button.tsx
export { Button, buttonVariants };

// Usage
import { Button } from "@dukkani/ui/components/button";
```

### Index Exports (Optional)

Some components may have index files for convenience:

```typescript
// packages/ui/src/components/index.ts
export { Button } from "./button";
export { Card } from "./card";
```

## Usage in Apps

### Import Pattern

```typescript
// Import from specific component file
import { Button } from "@dukkani/ui/components/button";
import { Card, CardContent, CardHeader } from "@dukkani/ui/components/card";

// Or from index if available
import { Button, Card } from "@dukkani/ui/components";
```

### Example

```typescript
// apps/dashboard/src/components/dashboard/orders/orders-list.tsx
import { Card, CardContent, CardHeader, CardTitle } from "@dukkani/ui/components/card";
import { Button } from "@dukkani/ui/components/button";

export default function OrdersList() {
  return (
    <Card>
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle>Orders</CardTitle>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <Button>Create Order</Button>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  );
}
```

